 ('113', '25', '4', '1', 'en_us', '7', '', '{\"typeId\":\"5\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Maintenance Technology \\/ Property Maintenance\",\"slug\":\"maintenance-technology-property-maintenance\",\"postDate\":1471094160,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>The Moore Tech Maintenance Technology course provides a student with the technical knowledge and ability to perform repairs on, and\\/or maintenance of property (buildings, both commercial and residential), as well as knowledge of management concepts.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Maintenance Technology students will be taught numerous repair skills in electricity, plumbing and carpentry that will provide each student with a well-rounded background in general repair and maintenance. The course includes classroom instruction and extensive hands-on instruction and shop experience.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Introduction to maintenance involving carpentry, piping, and plumbing is included.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Safety in use of hand and power tools<\\/li><li>Measuring, layout and cutting techniques<\\/li><li>Dry-wall repair<\\/li><li>Repair of door locks, doors and windows.<\\/li><li>Pipe cutting and threading and use of PVC pipe.<\\/li><li>Repairing leaky faucets<\\/li><li>Toilet replacement and repair<\\/li><li>Cleaning traps and repairing leaking pipes.<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Property Maintenance - Management<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Many students may be headed for a career as manager of a property maintenance staff. So training in management skills that include interviewing techniques, motivating and leading employees, preparing work schedules and preventive maintenance schedules, record keeping, inspections, parts ordering and inventory, and fair housing laws. Training in customer\\/tenant relations and communications that include writing reports, working with contractors and dealing with customer complaints.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Property Maintenance \\u2013 Electrical Repair (PM-111)<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Residential electrical including safety, electrical theory, terms and symbols, diagrams, repairing circuits, replacing switches, receptacles, and circuit breakers, low voltage circuits and inspection.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Property Maintenance \\u2013 Carpentry Repair (PM-112)<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Residential carpentry including safety, proper selection and use of tools, materials, measuring, cutting lumber, adhesives and fasteners, structural design, drywall repair, replacing locks and doors and residential inspection<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Property Maintenance \\u2013 Plumbing Repair (PM-113)<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Residential plumbing including safety, understanding basic plumbing systems, materials, PVC pipe, copper tubing, soldering, faucet repair, toilet repair, disposal installation, repairing leaks and residential inspection.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>* Visit the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.mynextmove.org\\/profile\\/summary\\/49-9042.00\\\">O*NET<\\/a>&nbsp;link or go to the Dept. of Labor resource center to view the employment outlook for this program.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>** Day program recommended electives include two courses in Industrial Electricity and Computer Operation.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.williamrmoore.org\\/sites\\/default\\/files\\/gainfulemployment\\/maint-tech-2012-13.pdf\\\">Gainful Employment Information For This Program<\\/a>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"7\":\"100\",\"5\":[\"26\",\"27\"],\"18\":\"The Moore Tech Maintenance Technology course provides a student with the technical knowledge and ability to perform repairs on, and\\/or maintenance of property (buildings, both commercial and residential), as well as knowledge of management concepts.\",\"6\":\"49-9042.00\",\"3\":\"<iframe width=\\\"560\\\" height=\\\"315\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/ExliFFoeddY\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allowfullscreen><\\/iframe>\"}}', '2016-08-13 21:22:40', '2016-08-13 21:22:40', 'e97eaa3b-56a4-4584-88b4-f29a870df0e5'),
 ('114', '20', '4', '1', 'en_us', '7', '', '{\"typeId\":\"5\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Machining Technology\\/Machine Shop\",\"slug\":\"machining-technology-machine-shop\",\"postDate\":1470534240,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p><strong>The Moore Tech Machining Technology\\/Machine Shop Program<\\/strong>&nbsp;has redesigned its curriculum to meet the needs of Memphis\' large and growing Medical Device Manufacturing industry. This program is taught in the most complete educational machine shop in the south with the most modern CNC machines. Courses provide the technical knowledge and fundamental experience necessary to perform machine shop work. Students learn to read and use blueprints skillfully, as well as hand tools and heavy machinery required to forge quality parts from metal.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Once students understand how to make metal parts with manual machines, students learn how to make metal parts with CNC Lathes and CNC Milling machines using our state-of-the-art computerized CNC machines. Our new Precision Medical Machining course familiarizes students with the skills, documentation and requirements needed by the large local medical device manufacturing industry.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Moore Tech training provides students the experience of actually performing in a working machine shop. Each student is given increasingly more challenging assignments according to his\\/her individual progress and ability. Students may accelerate according to their skills. A technician in the machine shop trade should have sound work habits, knowledge of mathematics and blueprint reading and be attentive to detail.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With the growing Medical Device Manufacturing Industry in Memphis as well as the other manufacturing, construction and service industries that need metal parts, Moore Tech\\u2019s program provides a student with the hands-on ability and confidence needed for successful employment in these industries.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.williamrmoore.org\\/programs\\/machine-shop\\/Machining-Brochure.pdf\\\">PDF Program Brochure<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>* Visit the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.mynextmove.org\\/profile\\/summary\\/51-4081.00\\\">O*NET<\\/a>&nbsp;link or go to the Dept. of Labor resource center to view the employment outlook for this program.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.williamrmoore.org\\/sites\\/default\\/files\\/gainfulemployment\\/machine-shop-2012-13.pdf\\\">Gainful Employment Information For This Program<\\/a><\\/p>\",\"7\":\"100\",\"5\":[\"17\",\"18\",\"19\"],\"18\":\"The Moore Tech Machining Technology\\/Machine Shop Program has redesigned its curriculum to meet the needs of Memphis\' large and growing Medical Device Manufacturing industry. This program is taught in the most complete educational machine shop in the south with the most modern CNC machines. Courses provide the technical knowledge and fundamental experience necessary to perform machine shop work.\",\"6\":\"51-4081.00\",\"3\":\"<iframe width=\\\"560\\\" height=\\\"315\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/NZVLVHr0cdc\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allowfullscreen><\\/iframe>\"}}', '2016-08-13 21:23:12', '2016-08-13 21:23:12', '6b4595d2-827b-453b-a5de-b3bc92d7f0f9'),
 ('115', '5', '4', '1', 'en_us', '6', '', '{\"typeId\":\"5\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Air Conditioning, Refrigeration and Heating\",\"slug\":\"test\",\"postDate\":1470512880,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<h2><strong>81% placement rates for graduates from this program.*<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>The Air Conditioning\\/Refrigeration and Heating Program<\\/strong>&nbsp;is focused on training service personnel for this field. The objective of the program is to provide a student with knowledge of the basic principles of air conditioning\\/refrigeration and heating mechanisms, their operation, maintenance, service and repair. A unique and vital benefit to Moore Tech students is the combination of classroom study with hands-on, working experience with modern equipment in completely furnished, individual heating lab and refrigeration & air conditioning lab. Moore Tech professional instructors impart the knowledge that creates the ability that builds the confidence a student needs to be successfully employed in the industry. After completing the program the individual should be an employable, competent service technician.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>* Visit the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.mynextmove.org\\/profile\\/summary\\/49-9021.00\\\">O*NET<\\/a>&nbsp;link or go to the Dept. of Labor resource center to view the employment outlook for this program.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.williamrmoore.org\\/sites\\/default\\/files\\/gainfulemployment\\/AC-2012-13.pdf\\\">Gainful Employment Information For This Program<\\/a><\\/p>\",\"7\":\"92\",\"5\":[\"8\",\"12\",\"11\"],\"18\":\"The Air Conditioning\\/Refrigeration and Heating Program is focused on training service personnel for this field. The objective of the program is to provide a student with knowledge of the basic principles of air conditioning\\/refrigeration and heating mechanisms, their operation, maintenance, service and repair.\",\"6\":\"49-9021.01\",\"19\":[\"99\"],\"3\":\"<iframe width=\\\"560\\\" height=\\\"315\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/evz13Th2gBQ\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allowfullscreen><\\/iframe>\"}}', '2016-08-13 21:34:19', '2016-08-13 21:34:19', '3dc8aad1-18b9-4433-a13a-a3a53d764d1f'),
