 ('5', 'field', '1', 'en_us', ' the air conditioning refrigeration and heating program is focused on training service personnel for this field the objective of the program is to provide a student with knowledge of the basic principles of air conditioning refrigeration and heating mechanisms their operation maintenance service and repair a unique and vital benefit to moore tech students is the combination of classroom study with hands on working experience with modern equipment in completely furnished individual heating lab and refrigeration air conditioning lab moore tech professional instructors impart the knowledge that creates the ability that builds the confidence a student needs to be successfully employed in the industry after completing the program the individual should be an employable competent service technician visit the o net link or go to the dept of labor resource center to view the employment outlook for this program '),
